SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

FROM (

    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]

SELECT [t].[AssignmentId], [t].[Title], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[QuestionText], [t0].[AnswerId], [t0].[OptionId], [t0].[OptionText], [t0].[c], [t0].[AnswerText]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AssignmentId], [a].[Title]
    FROM [Assignments] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AssignmentId] = @__command_AssignmentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[QuestionText], [a0].[AnswerId], [o].[OptionId], [o].[OptionText], CASE
        WHEN [a0].[AnswerId] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], [a0].[AnswerText], [q].[AssignmentId]
    FROM [questions] AS [q]
    LEFT JOIN [answer] AS [a0] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [a0].[QuestionId]
    LEFT JOIN [options] AS [o] ON [q].[QuestionId] = [o].[QuestionId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AssignmentId] = [t0].[AssignmentId]
ORDER BY [t].[AssignmentId], [t0].[QuestionId], [t0].[AnswerId]
